descriptionNullable:
### Context

Having a notetaker makes our life easy when we have to quickly review something. 2020 is the year of misfortune for all. Made an attempt to gather everything happened around India in the year 2020. This data collection is a part of the complete [project](https://github.com/keerthana-ceg/MIning_master)

### Content

The dataset has 366 days(leap year) news headlines(News column) starting from Jan1,2020 to Dec31,2020(Date column)

### Acknowledgements

Times of India website


### Inspiration

Is it possible to make a notepad with highlights of 2020?
title: 2020 News Headlines(English)
subtitle: News headlines for the year 2020
